      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility"> ¶ [Director forwds return showing saving of expenditure in 1870 as compared with 1869] ¶  ¶ The original estimates for 1870 (VictoriaParliamentary paperB 2, p. 12, ordered to be printed 8 March 1870)...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">70.05.03</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To James McCulloch</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">No. 4340, vol. 1870 W, VPRS 1168/P inward correspondence registers, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letter not<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>found; item is a register entry only, of a letter<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>dated<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>3 May 1870.</p>
               </note>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>[Director forwds return showing saving of expenditure in 1870 as compared with 1869]<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The original estimates for 1870 (Victoria<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Parliamentary paper</seg>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>B 2, p. 12, ordered to be printed 8 March 1870),<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>prepared by the Macpherson administration,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>showed a total of £5,650 for M's activities. However, savings were requested in all areas<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>by the McCulloch Government that took office in April. Although the request to M has not been found, in M to J. McCulloch, 23 April 1870 (in this edition as 70-04-23a),<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>M itemized his proposals for reducing the budget for 1870, amounting to a revised total of £4,990. M made no provision for the Inspector of Forests (William Ferguson). Revised estimates were published<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>on<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>17 May 1870 (<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Parliamentary paper</seg>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>B 60), showing an overall reduction in expenditure in the Chief Secretary's Department of £13,780, 2.1 percent of the March estimates. M's budget was reduced by 20 percent.</p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Compare the budgets passed by Parliament for M:</p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The approved budget for 1869 was £5230, under the following heads:</p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Government Botanist and Director of Botanic Gardens, with Quarters<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>610</p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Wages of Gardeners, Botanical Collector, Laborers, &amp;c.<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>3,680</p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Purchase of Plants and Seeds<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>150</p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Expense of publishing work on Australian Plants<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>150</p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Stores, Timber, Bricks, and Stationery<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>350</p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Forage for three (3) Cart Horses, &amp;c.<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>140</p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Transit and other Expenses<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>120</p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Travelling Expenses<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>40</p>
                     <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>That for 1870 was £4,176, under the following heads:</p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Government Botanist and Director of Botanic Gardens, &amp;c, with Quarters<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>610</p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Inspector of Forests (with Quarters)*<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>250</p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>*This officer also performs the duties of Principal Assistant at the Botanic Gardens</p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Wages of Gardeners, Botanical Collector, Laborers, &amp;c.<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>2,691</p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Purchase of Plants and Seeds and Expense of publishing work</p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>on Australian Plants<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>130<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Stores, Timber, Bricks, and Stationery<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>250<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Forage for two Cart Horses<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>85<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Transit and Incidental Expenses<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>120<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Travelling Expenses<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>40</p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>(Respectively, Victoria.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Votes and proceedings of the Legislative Assembly</seg>, 1869, vol.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>1, p. 51; 1870, session 1, vol. 1, p. 86, approved 31 May 1870.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
